CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in advertisement in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 10, 1945, pg. 21, reads: "Who will be Miss Pin-Up at the semi-formal pin-up dance - Seated left to right: Katherine Morris, Dorothy Butler, Evelyn Ormes.  Standing, left to right: Vermal Johnson, Connie Harris, Esther Austin, Footie Ferguson, Lee Anna Collins, Rosemarie Horn, Katherine Harp..."
TitMainTitle: "Miss Pin-Up" contestants, seated from left: Katherine Morris, Dorothy Butler, Evelyn Ormes; standing: Vermal Johnson, Connie Harris, Esther Austin, Footie Ferguson, Lee Anna Collins, Rosemarie Horn, and Katherine Harp, posed in interior with striped curtains
